overview.en: GKBLOCK is a public chain project focusing on the commercial application of encrypted futures payment assets industry. It is a decentralized intelligent futures platform based on the block chain network for collaborative operation, providing users with accurate services related to the issuance, trading and management of futures payment assets.
overview.zh: GKBLOCK是一个专注于加密期货支付资产行业商业应用的公有链项目，是一个基于区块链网络进行协同操作，为用户精准提供期货支付资产发行、交易及管理相关服务的去中心化的智能期货平台。
